## Known vite.config issue caught and fixed

researcher.out had `outDir: '../../../michaelwegter.com/...'` (3 levels up). Correct path from `demo-src` is 4 levels up (`'../../../../michaelwegter.com/...'`). Fixed in vite.config.js before final build. First build went to `upwork-agentic-workflow/michaelwegter.com/` (wrong), cleaned up.

