- decisions: localStorage/SEED_LEADS fallback when API unavailable (no CORS issue in iframe); WebGPU iframe warning shows "Open Full Demo" link; SmolVLM loaded lazily (import() inside runAudit, not top-level); 4 levels up in outDir (not 3)
